entry.title: Bitcoin core 0.11.0 release candidate 1 available
entry.summary: A new release of Bitcoin Core 0.11.0rc1 executables has been uploaded by Wladimir to https://bitcoin.org/bin/bitcoin-core-0.11.0/test/. The source code can be found in the source tarball or in git under the tag 'v0.11.0rc1'. Preliminary release notes are available at https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/blob/0.11/doc/release-notes.md. Wladimir thanked everyone who participated in development or the gitian build process.
